<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3805837>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Begonia harauensis Girm. sp. nov. A. Habit (Lembah Harau Nature Reserve, Hughes, M. & Taufiq, A. MH 1556). B. Male inflorescence. C. Male flower. D. Pair of female flowers showing ovary. E. Unripe fruit. Insets from plant cultivated in Bogor Botanical Garden (accession number B200608257/ JS 436, derived from material collected in Lembah Harau). Scale bars on insets = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3805837/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

